{"id": 2393, "genre": 1001, "title": "在社交网络上，有哪些让你感觉“仿佛生活在平行世界”的时刻？", "description": "互联网上的哪些瞬间，让你察觉到“原来世界还有这一面”？（图片来自：iStock © ah_designs）", "record_count": 5051, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180605165926q8PiSpRuOBD9bVUl.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-07T03:03:26Z", "options": [{"id": 286208, "content": "从认真玩过啥游戏，却聊得很专业", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368377}, {"id": 285953, "content": "氪金！除了氪金你别想好好玩游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367304}, {"id": 285954, "content": "追星吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1353570}, {"id": 285957, "content": "我是一个在一个故事中的人，假设。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1349179}, {"id": 286213, "content": "在别的地方高考的基友面临被社会人士踹凳子抄题甚至用刀子威胁的危险。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217164}, {"id": 286726, "content": "红海行动    然而没看过", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372032}, {"id": 285960, "content": "翻着评论看到了两次101，都没明白是个啥，直到我百度之后……", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 951650}, {"id": 285961, "content": "连创造101都不知道的人，是不是会对虚拟偶像和地下女团，感觉像在听什么怪事奇闻？", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132121}, {"id": 285962, "content": "在朋友圈转发评论一些社会新闻的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194124}, {"id": 285963, "content": "室友们聊的创造101明星大冒险之类的综艺表示听不懂插不进去话", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1330997}, {"id": 286220, "content": "平时八竿子打不着的人，他们三观不合、思想深度不一，却突然有了一个对话的平台，当然大部分时候只会发生一场毫无营养的鸡同鸭讲，过程宛若骂街。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276858}, {"id": 286223, "content": "只要你diss杨超越\n我们就还是朋友\n（谁？？在说谁？？为什么？？）", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1361926}, {"id": 288271, "content": "太过美好的时候，心生向往，转念一想，现实哪会这样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378608}, {"id": 285968, "content": "创造101是新女团吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366956}, {"id": 285970, "content": "网络上看到一些很热很火的软件、综艺、人物等等。但丝毫没有想要去深入了解。", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367624}, {"id": 285972, "content": "一些没营养的视频占据了我们的时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096851}, {"id": 285988, "content": "各种各样网红，你怎么说？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289848}, {"id": 287782, "content": "仿佛全世界都在看快手抖音，就我一个人用着别的app", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1338936}, {"id": 287527, "content": "现如今的多数APP离公共领域越来越远，担心自己有一天会娱乐至死，所以选择让其成为平行世界。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374149}, {"id": 286515, "content": "王？一？这？这！鬯", "image": "img/option/option/20180611155940WeJ14Eo6KPYCuhrn.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371303}, {"id": 286516, "content": "一觉醒来别人都在讨论比特币和区块链的时候 这都特么是啥啊……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371307}, {"id": 288820, "content": "真好，这里的人都好相似", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380805}, {"id": 286267, "content": "三观的差异", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368706}, {"id": 286526, "content": "丝。。这", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371303}, {"id": 286527, "content": "你在干嘛？你是", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371303}, {"id": 286023, "content": "老铁没毛病 双击666", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366244}, {"id": 286282, "content": "B站是啥？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368856}, {"id": 287564, "content": "创造101", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1375995}, {"id": 292941, "content": "不喜欢喊麦，更讨厌用经典的纯音乐做背景的喊麦。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670771}, {"id": 287066, "content": "蔡徐坤是谁？EXO和TFboys呢？解散了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358229}, {"id": 286043, "content": "当大家都觉得快手是一个垃圾平台的时候，我觉得快手是未来的中国大学慕课", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1361722}, {"id": 286044, "content": "创造101\n偶像练习生", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367645}, {"id": 289118, "content": "别人：”这人好帅！你看你看！ 是不是超级帅的！”我：“呃呃呃，还行。。。。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1383291}, {"id": 286047, "content": "我 与 上司", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367647}, {"id": 286049, "content": "所以创造101到底是个啥？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047265}, {"id": 286050, "content": "聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1349845}, {"id": 286052, "content": "不喜欢听歌时，有人总是说这是抖音，快手上来的。还有的歌直接被冠上“抖音最火歌”的名字。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367651}, {"id": 286055, "content": "各种练习生偶像团…", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324440}, {"id": 286311, "content": "看小红书才知道什么是生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098071}, {"id": 287094, "content": "比如某天的工体三里屯某天的图书馆某天的五道口，某日下午的文学书籍，动漫和夜里的肥皂剧，网络里无忧无虑的人真实存在吗，从另一个情景抽离出来 进入另一个状态里的时候总有一种熟悉的陌生感，原来身边还有这种地方，原来还有这种生活方式，这大概就是平行世界的感觉，每天都那么不真实又混乱。", "image": "img/option/option/20180613202334teWwUnL7ivZTR98l", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373408}, {"id": 288631, "content": "童叟无欺，实事求是", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380063}, {"id": 296311, "content": "101", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047305}, {"id": 286328, "content": "自从接触到Tumblr和VPN，我觉得世界就是平行世界。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1369213}, {"id": 286073, "content": "从来没有下过抖音快手……", "image": null, "praise_count": 65, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367640}, {"id": 286074, "content": "101？？？101忠狗那部电影吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367681}, {"id": 286076, "content": "明星原来真的很能赚钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367694}, {"id": 285309, "content": "同一部电影，在朋友圈和电影网站的评分很低，但票房却非常高", "image": null, "praise_count": 136, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 285310, "content": "对某些公共事件，微博上可能已经吵翻了，朋友圈里却很安静", "image": null, "praise_count": 290, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 286078, "content": "微博热搜中的丑闻一天一个样，还没有搞明白事情来龙去脉，下一个热搜又出现了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1104040}, {"id": 285311, "content": "热搜里永远是自己不关心的话题，点进去看到上万的转发量", "image": null, "praise_count": 449, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}]}